<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <p xml:id="PN249-intro">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai.<gap quantity="12" reason="lost" unit="character"/>tumpi cōkīraṉār pāṭiyatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PN249">
<l>katirmūk kāral kīḻccēṟ ṟoḷippak</l>
<l>kaṇaikōṭṭu vāḷai mīṉīrp piṟaḻa</l>
<l>verippūm paḻaṉa nerittuṭaṉ valaiña</l>
<l>rarikkuraṟ ṟaṭāriyiṉ yāmai miḷirap</l>
<l>paṉainukum paṉṉa ciṉaimutir varālō</l>
<l>ṭuṟaḻvē laṉṉa voṇkayaṉ mukakku</l>
<l>makaṉāṭ ṭaṇṇal pukavē neruṉaip</l>
<l>pakaliṭaṅ kaṇṇip palaroṭuṅ kūṭi</l>
<l>yoruvaḻip paṭṭaṉṟu maṉṉē yiṉṟē</l>
<l>yaṭaṅkiya kaṟpi ṉāynutaṉ maṭantai</l>
<l>yuyarnilai yulaka mavaṉpuka<gap quantity="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/>lari</l>
<l>nīṟāṭu cuḷakiṟ cīṟiṭa nīkki</l>
<l>yaḻuta lāṉāk kaṇṇaṇ</l>
<l>meḻuku māppikaṇ kaluḻnī rāṉē.</l>
</lg>
<lg xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="7">Yesterday, the entering of the majesty of [this] wide land, (7ab+d)</l>
<l corresp="1">where, while ray-nosed Āral fish hide below in the mire, </l>
<l corresp="2">while round-finned Vāḷai fish leap above the water, </l>
<l corresp="3">those with nets, crushing together through the paddy field with flaming flowers </l>
<l corresp="4">so that tortoises [shaped] like harsh-voice Taṭāri drums roll over </l>
<l corresp="6">draw out bright carp that are like rivalling spears </l>
<l corresp="5">together with Varāl fish who ripen eggs [shaped] like soft leaves of palmyra, </l>
<l corresp="8">joining with all the many with chaplets from various places </l>
<l corresp="9">happened on one way [with them]. Today </l>
<l corresp="10">[this] girl with a choice forehead and quiet fidelity, </l>
<l corresp="11a-c">as he entered the world of high standing, </l>
<l corresp="11d-12">clears a place as small as a winnowing fan bathed in itching dust </l>
<l corresp="13">[and] with eyes that do not stop crying </l>
<l corresp="14">smears [its] with cowdung with [the help] of the tears that dim [her] eyes. </l>
</lg>
